headline: A Fresh Look at Realty Income (O) Valuation as Investor Interest Grows
summary: Realty Income (O) has once again caught investors’ attention, but not because of any headline-grabbing event or dramatic announcement. Instead, the spotlight has turned to the stock as it continues to quietly move within its established range. This raises an important question for anyone holding or eyeing shares: is this just another period of steady performance or a subtle signal of changing value? This interest comes as Realty Income’s share price is essentially flat over the past year...
